author: Erika Edwards
title: Delirium, other brain changes may be signs of coronavirus
description: Some COVID-19 patients have brain changes, including delirium and stroke. Can coronavirus infect the brain? What does coronavirus do to the brain?
content:
Nicole Hutcherson first noticed something was wrong with her father normally a spry early-riser who enjoyed yard work and home renovation projects earlier this month, when he wasn't getting out of bed until nearly midday.
